#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:2
msgid "手动编程与编辑工具"
msgstr "Manual Programming and Editing Tools"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:4
msgid "本节概述自动编程完成后从标记对齐、模板审查、手动补录的完整操作讲解。"
msgstr ""
"This section walks through everything you do after Auto-Programming finishes"
" — mark alignment, template review, and manual entry."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:11
msgid "标记 / 对齐 PCB（简介）"
msgstr "Mark / Align PCB (brief)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:13
msgid ""
"标记 / 对齐 PCB 的完整说明（mark 点添加、AI 算法与模板匹配切换、独特标记、二值化抽色等）请参见 "
":doc:`mark_align_pcb` 页面。"
msgstr ""
"Full instructions for Mark / Align PCB — adding Mark Points, switching "
"between the AI algorithm and Template Match, Unique Markers, and color-range"
" binarization — live on the :doc:`mark_align_pcb` page."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:16
msgid "模板编辑器"
msgstr "Template Editor"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:18
msgid "**进入模板编辑器**"
msgstr "**Open the Template Editor**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:20
msgid ""
"在编程页面（Teach）左侧标签栏切换至 **元件** 标签后，主视图即为模板编辑器（Template "
"Editor）。模板编辑器左侧为元件列表面板，右侧为画布区域。"
msgstr ""
"On the Teach page, switch to the **Component** tab in the left tab strip; "
"the main view becomes the Template Editor. The component list sits on the "
"left, the canvas on the right."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:22
msgid "进入模板编辑器时，若产品存在不健康元件，系统会弹出警告提示："
msgstr ""
"When you enter the Template Editor and the product still has unhealthy "
"components, the system pops a warning:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:-1
msgid "警告示例"
msgstr "Warning example"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:28
msgid "点击\"确认\"后可以继续操作。"
msgstr "Click *Confirm* to proceed."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:30
msgid "**画布区域顶栏开关**"
msgstr "**Top-of-canvas switches**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:32
msgid "画布顶栏提供两个功能开关："
msgstr "The canvas top bar offers two switches:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:34
msgid ""
"**平移所有元件（Translate All "
"Components）**：启用后，拖动画布上任意元件将同步平移产品内所有元件及其特征，适用于全局位置校正。"
msgstr ""
"**Translate All Components**: when on, dragging any component on the canvas "
"translates every component and feature in the product together — useful for "
"a global position correction."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:35
msgid ""
"**显示抽色二值化（Show Color Range Binary "
"Mask）**：启用后，在当前选中特征上叠加显示颜色范围二值化掩码，辅助颜色参数调整。"
msgstr ""
"**Show Color Range Binary Mask**: when on, overlays the binarized color-"
"range mask on the currently-selected feature — helps tune color parameters."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:37
msgid "**绘制工具栏**"
msgstr "**Drawing toolbar**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:39
msgid "画布右侧为垂直排列的绘制工具栏。工具说明如下（括号内为快捷键）："
msgstr ""
"The vertical drawing toolbar sits on the right side of the canvas. The tools"
" and their keyboard shortcuts (in parentheses):"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:41
msgid ""
"**选择（Select，快捷键 "
"V）**：左键点击或框选画布上的特征/元件；左键拖拽空白区域可框选多个未分组的检测框；中键拖拽平移；滚轮缩放。右键在选中对象上唤出右键菜单。"
msgstr ""
"**Select (V)**: left-click or drag-select features and components on the "
"canvas; left-drag on empty space selects multiple ungrouped inspection "
"boxes; middle-drag pans; scroll wheel zooms. Right-click on a selected "
"object opens the context menu."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:42
msgid "**平移/缩放（Pan/Zoom，快捷键 H）**：按住任意鼠标键平移视图；滚轮缩放；用于纯浏览，不影响选择操作。"
msgstr ""
"**Pan / Zoom (H)**: hold any mouse button to pan the view; scroll wheel "
"zooms. Pure browsing — leaves the selection alone."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:43
msgid "**添加本体检测（Add Body Feature，快捷键 1）**：绘制主体（本体/贴装）检测框。"
msgstr "**Add Body Feature (1)**: draw a body (mounting) inspection box."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:44
msgid "**添加焊锡检测（Add Solder Feature，快捷键 2）**：绘制焊点/焊锡检测框。"
msgstr "**Add Solder Feature (2)**: draw a solder-joint inspection box."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:45
msgid "**添加IC引脚检测（Add Lead Feature，快捷键 3）**：绘制整排的IC引脚检测框，框选后可右键复制/旋转用于其它边。"
msgstr ""
"**Add Lead Feature (3)**: draw an IC-lead inspection box spanning one row of"
" leads; right-click the result to copy / rotate it for the other sides."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:46
msgid "**添加文本检测（Add Text Feature，快捷键 4）**：标注丝印、字符、批次/日期等需要 OCR 识别的区域。"
msgstr ""
"**Add Text Feature (4)**: mark silkscreen text, characters, batch / date "
"codes, and anything else that needs OCR."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:47
msgid "**添加条形码检测（Add Barcode Feature，快捷键 5）**：绘制条形码检测区域，用于 PCB 序列号追溯。"
msgstr ""
"**Add Barcode Feature (5)**: draw a barcode inspection region for PCB "
"serial-number traceability."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:48
msgid "**添加DIP焊点特征（Add DIP Solder Feature）**：绘制 DIP 插件焊点检测框。"
msgstr ""
"**Add DIP Solder Feature**: draw a DIP through-hole solder-joint inspection "
"box."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:49
msgid "**添加桥接检测（Add Bridge Feature）**：绘制焊桥（solder bridge）检测区域。"
msgstr "**Add Bridge Feature**: draw a solder-bridge inspection region."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:50
msgid "**焊盘沾胶检测（Red Glue on Pad Feature，快捷键 8）**：绘制焊盘沾红胶检测区域。"
msgstr ""
"**Red Glue on Pad Feature (8)**: draw an inspection region for red glue on "
"the solder pad."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:51
msgid "**颜色检测（Color Inspection Feature，快捷键 9）**：绘制通用颜色区域检测框。"
msgstr ""
"**Color Inspection Feature (9)**: draw a general-purpose color-region "
"inspection box."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:53
msgid "各检测工具的具体检测参数说明见 :ref:`检测工具参考` 中各工具页面。"
msgstr ""
"Per-tool inspection parameters are documented on each tool's page under "
":ref:`检测工具参考`."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:55
msgid "**重新定义检测区域**"
msgstr "**Redefine Inspection Region**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:57
msgid ""
"当自动编程结果整体不理想（漏识别区域较多、检测框生成质量差）时，可点击页面上方的 **重新定义检测区域** 按钮，重新框选 PCB "
"上的有效检测区域。点击此按钮会触发一次完整的\"重做自动编程\"流程："
msgstr ""
"When the Auto-Programming result is poor overall (many missed regions, low-"
"quality inspection boxes), click **Redefine Inspection Region** at the top "
"to re-box the effective inspection area on the PCB. This button triggers a "
"full *redo Auto-Programming* flow:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:59
msgid "删除现有的 **全部检测框**\\ （含 mark 点 / 独特标记）。"
msgstr ""
"Removes **every existing inspection box** (including Mark Points and Unique "
"Markers)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:60
msgid "在新框选的区域上重新执行自动编程，生成新的检测框集合。"
msgstr ""
"Re-runs Auto-Programming on the new region and produces a fresh set of "
"inspection boxes."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:61
msgid "自动触发 **自动生成检测参数** 与 **评估全部** 步骤。"
msgstr ""
"Automatically triggers the **Auto-generate Inspection Parameters** and "
"**Evaluate All** steps."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:65
msgid ""
"**重新定义检测区域** 是破坏性操作：现有所有 mark "
"点、检测框与人工调整都会被清空。如仅需在局部区域补充检测框，建议用工具栏中的对应绘制工具（本体 / 焊锡 / IC 引脚 "
"等）手动绘制单个检测框，避免清空整板。"
msgstr ""
"**Redefine Inspection Region is destructive**: every existing Mark Point, "
"inspection box, and manual adjustment is wiped. If you only need to add a "
"few inspection boxes in a small area, draw them manually with the matching "
"toolbar tool (Body / Solder / IC Lead, etc.) instead of clearing the entire "
"board."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:67
msgid "关于画布快捷键，参考 :ref:`编程页面快捷键`。"
msgstr "For the full canvas keyboard reference, see :ref:`编程页面快捷键`."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:70
msgid "元件列表"
msgstr "Component list"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:72
msgid "**分组模式**"
msgstr "**Grouping modes**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:74
msgid "元件列表面板顶部提供三个分组选项卡："
msgstr "Three grouping tabs sit at the top of the component-list panel:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:76
msgid "**元件（Component）**：以单个元件（位号/标识）为粒度显示列表，每行对应一个独立元件。这是默认模式。"
msgstr ""
"**Component**: lists components at the per-designator level; one row per "
"component. Default mode."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:77
msgid "**料号（Part）**：按 ``part_no`` （料号）合并同类元件，显示该料号下的元件总数及汇总状态。"
msgstr ""
"**Part**: groups by ``part_no``; each row shows the total component count "
"under that PN and the aggregated status."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:78
msgid "**封装（Package）**：按 ``package_no`` （封装型号）分组合并，适合批量查看同封装的检测状态。"
msgstr ""
"**Package**: groups by ``package_no``; convenient for batch-reviewing the "
"inspection status of every component sharing a package."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:80
msgid "点击列表中的某一条目，画布会自动定位并高亮对应元件或特征。"
msgstr ""
"Clicking a list entry pans and highlights the corresponding component or "
"feature on the canvas."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:82
msgid "**搜索与过滤**"
msgstr "**Search and filter**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:84
msgid "列表上方提供搜索栏，支持按位号（标识）、料号、封装号进行文字搜索。搜索栏还提供以下过滤标签（可多选）："
msgstr ""
"The search bar above the list supports text search by designator, part "
"number, and package number, plus the following filter tags (multi-select):"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:86
msgid "**健康（Healthy）/ 不健康（Unhealthy）**：按元件健康状态过滤（互斥）。"
msgstr ""
"**Healthy / Unhealthy**: filter by component health (mutually exclusive)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:87
msgid "**复评通过（Reevaluation Pass）/ 复评失败（Reevaluation Fail）**：按训练集重新评估结果过滤（互斥）。"
msgstr ""
"**Reevaluation Pass / Reevaluation Fail**: filter by the most recent "
"training-set re-evaluation result (mutually exclusive)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:88
msgid "**仅坏板标记（Badmark only）/ 排除坏板标记（Exclude badmark）**：按是否为坏板标记元件过滤（互斥）。"
msgstr ""
"**Badmark only / Exclude badmark**: filter by whether the component is a "
"badmark (mutually exclusive)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:89
msgid "其它可用过滤标签（如 **未分组特征** 等）出现在同一搜索栏下拉中。"
msgstr ""
"Additional filter tags (such as **Ungrouped Features**) appear in the same "
"search-bar drop-down."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:91
msgid "**显示内容**"
msgstr "**What the list shows**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:93
msgid "若已上传 CAD，元件名称会同时显示丝印/标识。列表每行显示该元件的检测状态（通过/不通过/未训练/健康状态等）。"
msgstr ""
"When CAD has been uploaded, the component name shows the silkscreen / "
"designator alongside. Each row also displays the component's inspection "
"status (passed / failed / untrained / health state)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:-1
msgid "元件列表示例"
msgstr "Component-list example"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:-1
msgid "搜索示例"
msgstr "Search example"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:104
msgid "画布交互"
msgstr "Canvas interaction"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:106
msgid "**选择、变换与绘制模式**"
msgstr "**Select, Transform, and Draw modes**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:108
msgid "模板编辑器画布有三类主要操作模式，通过右侧工具栏切换："
msgstr ""
"The Template Editor canvas has three primary modes, switched from the right-"
"hand toolbar:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:110
msgid ""
"**选择模式（Select，V）**：点击或框选对象；不可直接拖动调整大小/位置（特征框处于锁定可点击但不可拖动状态）。选中后可通过右键菜单操作。"
msgstr ""
"**Select mode (V)**: click or drag-select objects; size and position cannot "
"be changed by direct dragging — feature boxes are clickable but locked "
"against motion. Use the right-click menu after selecting."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:111
msgid "**变换模式（Pan/Zoom，H）**：纯视图平移/缩放，不影响任何对象选择。"
msgstr ""
"**Pan / Zoom mode (H)**: view-only pan and zoom; leaves object selection "
"alone."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:112
msgid ""
"**绘制模式**：选中任意绘制工具（本体/焊锡/IC引脚等）后，左键在空白区域拖拽即可绘制新检测框；绘制完成后自动切换为可编辑状态。在绘制模式下，已有对象可被选中并拖拽调整（变换模式，鼠标变为调整手柄）。"
msgstr ""
"**Draw mode**: pick any drawing tool (Body / Solder / IC Lead / ...) and "
"left-drag on empty space to draw a new inspection box; the box becomes "
"editable as soon as you release. In Draw mode, existing objects can also be "
"selected and dragged to adjust — the cursor changes to the resize handles "
"when you hover them."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:114
msgid "**右键菜单**"
msgstr "**Right-click menu**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:116
msgid "在画布上右键点击选中的对象，会弹出上下文菜单，菜单项根据当前选中类型而不同："
msgstr ""
"Right-clicking a selected object opens the context menu. Its entries vary by"
" what's selected:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:118
msgid "**选中单个已分组元件时：**"
msgstr "**On a single grouped component:**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:120
msgid "**复制元件（Copy Component）**：进入粘贴预览模式，可在指定位置粘贴副本。"
msgstr ""
"**Copy Component**: enters paste-preview mode so you can place a copy at a "
"chosen position."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:121
msgid ""
"**取消分组特征（Ungroup Features）**：解散元件分组，将其下所有特征还原为未分组状态（仅对 array_index 0 "
"或未编入拼板的元件可见）。"
msgstr ""
"**Ungroup Features**: dissolve the component grouping and return its "
"features to ungrouped state (only shown on the base sub-board (``array_index"
" = 0``) or on components that aren't part of a panel)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:122
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:137
msgid "**向右旋转90°（Rotate 90° Right）**"
msgstr "**Rotate 90° Right**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:123
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:138
msgid "**向左旋转90°（Rotate 90° Left）**"
msgstr "**Rotate 90° Left**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:124
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:139
msgid "**旋转180°（Rotate 180°）**"
msgstr "**Rotate 180°**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:125
msgid "**删除元件（Remove Component）**：删除元件及其所有特征。"
msgstr ""
"**Remove Component**: delete the component along with every feature under "
"it."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:126
msgid ""
"**添加到私有库（Add to Private Library）/ 保存到私有库（Save to Private "
"Library）**：将该元件模板保存至私有模板库，供其它产品复用。"
msgstr ""
"**Add to Private Library / Save to Private Library**: save the component "
"template into the private library for reuse on other products."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:128
msgid "**选中多个元件时（框选多元件）：**"
msgstr "**On a multi-component selection (drag-selected components):**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:130
msgid "**标记为NG（Mark as NG）**、**取消NG标记（Unmark as NG）**：批量操作子阵列中元件的 NG 状态。"
msgstr ""
"**Mark as NG / Unmark as NG**: batch-toggle the NG status of components in "
"the selection (sub-array siblings included)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:131
msgid ""
"**跳过检测（Skip inspection）（N）**、**清除跳过检测（Clear skip "
"inspection）（N）**：批量设置或清除跳过检测标记（坏板标记元件除外）。详见 :ref:`元件配置` 中的\"跳过检测\"说明。"
msgstr ""
"**Skip inspection (N) / Clear skip inspection (N)**: batch-set or clear the "
"skip-inspection flag (badmark components excluded). See *Skip inspection* in"
" :ref:`元件配置` for details."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:132
msgid "**复制元件（Copy Component）（N）**"
msgstr "**Copy Component (N)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:133
msgid "**删除（Remove）（N）**"
msgstr "**Remove (N)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:135
msgid "**选中已分组元件内的某个特征时：**"
msgstr "**On a feature inside a grouped component:**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:140
msgid "**应用参数到同类型（Apply Params to Same Type）**：将当前特征的检测参数批量同步到该产品所有同类型特征。"
msgstr ""
"**Apply Params to Same Type**: copy this feature's inspection parameters to "
"every feature of the same type in the product."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:141
msgid "**删除（Remove）**"
msgstr "**Remove**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:143
msgid "**选中一组未分组特征时（featureGroup）：**"
msgstr "**On an ungrouped-feature group:**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:145
msgid "**旋转**：向右旋转90°、向左旋转90°、旋转180°（仅选中单个特征时显示）"
msgstr ""
"**Rotate**: 90° Right, 90° Left, 180° (only shown on a single-feature "
"selection)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:146
msgid ""
"**将选中的特征分组为新元件（Group selection as new component）**：打开分组对话框，填写标识等信息后创建新元件。"
msgstr ""
"**Group selection as new component**: opens the grouping dialog; fill in the"
" designator and other info to create a new component."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:147
msgid ""
"**组合为坏板标记（Combine into "
"badmark）**：在满足条件时显示（所选特征不含跨子板实例且不属于共享面板区域）。选中单个未分组特征时同样显示此项。"
msgstr ""
"**Combine into badmark**: shown when eligible — the selected features must "
"not span sub-board instances and must not belong to a shared-panel region. "
"Also shown on a single ungrouped feature."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:148
msgid "**复制（Copy）（N）**"
msgstr "**Copy (N)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:149
msgid "**删除（Delete）（N）**"
msgstr "**Delete (N)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:151
msgid "**右键空白画布时：**"
msgstr "**On a blank-canvas right-click:**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:153
msgid "**粘贴元件（Paste Component）（N）**：若剪贴板中有已复制的元件，在右键位置粘贴。"
msgstr ""
"**Paste Component (N)**: if a component is on the clipboard, paste it at the"
" right-click location."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:156
msgid ""
"**组合为坏板标记** 功能仅对未分组特征生效。已属于某元件的特征需在 :ref:`元件配置` "
"的元件信息面板中通过\"元件类型\"选择器将其设为坏板标记。"
msgstr ""
"**Combine into badmark** only works on ungrouped features. Features already "
"inside a component must be converted via the *Component Type* selector in "
"the Component Info panel — see :ref:`元件配置`."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:159
msgid "整板检测（简介）"
msgstr "Whole Board Inspection (brief)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:161
msgid "整板检测（包含 / 排除区域、表面污染检测等）的完整说明请参见 :doc:`whole_board_inspection` 页面。"
msgstr ""
"The full reference for Whole Board Inspection — Include / Exclude Regions, "
"Surface Contamination, and so on — lives on the "
":doc:`whole_board_inspection` page."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:164
msgid "检测设置（子板判废逻辑）"
msgstr "Inspection Settings (sub-board verdict logic)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:166
msgid "检测设置（比例模式 / badmark 模式 / 子板判废逻辑）的完整说明见 :ref:`产品设置（Recipe）` 页面的\"检测设置\"部分。"
msgstr ""
"The full reference for Inspection Settings — ratio mode, badmark mode, and "
"sub-board verdict logic — is in the *Inspection Settings* section of "
":ref:`产品设置（Recipe）`."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:169
msgid "健康性核对"
msgstr "Health review"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:171
msgid "训练前检查："
msgstr "Pre-training checks:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:173
msgid "基础信息：确认，或者按需录入 标识（丝印）、封装、料号（PN）。"
msgstr ""
"Basic info: confirm or fill in designator (silkscreen), package, and part "
"number."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst
msgid "组件属性填写示例"
msgstr "Filling in component properties — example"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:179
msgid "全板预览：是否存在缺失、漂移、超大/超小框。"
msgstr ""
"Full-board preview: scan for missing boxes, drifted boxes, oversized or "
"undersized boxes."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:180
msgid "局部密集区：是否重叠、是否覆盖相邻器件。"
msgstr ""
"Dense local areas: check for overlap or boxes that bleed onto neighbouring "
"parts."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:181
msgid "不健康列表：低置信度 / CAD 未匹配 / 尺寸异常。"
msgstr ""
"Unhealthy list: low confidence, unmatched CAD entries, anomalous sizes."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:183
msgid "正确但标为不健康：若位置无误可点击列表边上的 ``?`` 直接确认恢复为健康。"
msgstr ""
"Correct but marked unhealthy: if the position is fine, click the ``?`` next "
"to the row and confirm it back to healthy."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst
msgid "不健康元件示例"
msgstr "Unhealthy-component example"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:189
msgid "CAD 中存在但未检测：若实板缺失则忽略；若实际存在则手动补录。"
msgstr ""
"Present in CAD but not detected: if the physical board lacks the part, "
"ignore it; if the part is actually there, add it manually."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst
msgid "缺失标记示例"
msgstr "Missing-mark example"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:195
msgid "自动编程误检时：删除并重新手动补录。"
msgstr "Auto-Programming false positives: delete and re-add by hand."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:197
msgid "**确认所有不确定的元件为可信**"
msgstr "**Confirm all uncertain components as trusted**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:199
msgid ""
"页面顶部工具栏提供 **确认所有不确定的元件为可信** "
"按钮。当自动编程完成后，部分元件可能被标记为\"不确定\"（橙色或灰色提示，表示自动编程对该元件分类信心不足）。逐一手动确认这类元件会很耗时。点击此按钮会一次性把列表中所有\"不确定\"的元件批量确认为可信，并按当前自动编程结果保留它们的检测框与属性。"
msgstr ""
"The top toolbar exposes a **Confirm all uncertain components as trusted** "
"button. After Auto-Programming, some components may be flagged *uncertain* "
"(orange or gray, meaning Auto-Programming wasn't confident in its "
"classification). Confirming each one by hand is tedious; this button "
"confirms every *uncertain* component on the list in one batch and keeps "
"Auto-Programming's inspection boxes and properties intact."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:203
msgid ""
"建议在使用前先按 **不确定** "
"状态筛选元件列表，快速浏览这些元件的检测框是否合理；如果发现明显错误的元件，先单独删除或修改再点击批量确认，避免把错误的检测框一并保留。"
msgstr ""
"Before clicking it, filter the component list by *uncertain* status and skim"
" each component's inspection box; if any are obviously wrong, delete or fix "
"them individually first so the batch confirm doesn't preserve the bad boxes."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:208
msgid "手动编程工具栏"
msgstr "Manual programming toolbar"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:210
msgid "右侧工具栏包含："
msgstr "The toolbar on the right contains:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:-1
msgid "手动编程工具栏示例"
msgstr "Manual programming toolbar — example"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:216
msgid "**选择工具（V）**：左键拖拽框选多项未分组的检测框，右键唤出菜单，可分组合并为元件；中键拖拽平移；滚轮缩放。"
msgstr ""
"**Select (V)**: left-drag to select multiple ungrouped inspection boxes; "
"right-click opens the menu where you can group them into a component; "
"middle-drag pans; scroll wheel zooms."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:217
msgid "**拖拽工具（H）**：按住任意鼠标键平移视图；滚轮缩放；用于纯浏览不影响选择。"
msgstr ""
"**Pan (H)**: hold any mouse button to pan the view; scroll wheel zooms. Pure"
" browsing — leaves the selection alone."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:218
msgid "**本体工具（1）**：绘制主体检测框（Mounting）。"
msgstr "**Body (1)**: draw a body / mounting inspection box."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:219
msgid "**焊料工具（2）**：绘制焊料检测框（Solder 2D）。"
msgstr "**Solder (2)**: draw a Solder 2D inspection box."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:220
msgid "**引脚工具（3）**：绘制整排的引脚检测框（IC Lead）；框选后可右键复制 / 旋转用于其它侧。"
msgstr ""
"**Lead (3)**: draw an IC-lead inspection box that spans one row; right-click"
" to copy / rotate it for the other sides."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:221
msgid "**文本工具（4）**：标注丝印、字符、批次 / 日期等需要 OCR 的区域。"
msgstr ""
"**Text (4)**: mark silkscreen text, characters, batch / date codes, and "
"anything else that needs OCR."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:222
msgid "**条形码工具（5）**：绘制条形码检测区域，用于 PCB 序列号追溯。"
msgstr ""
"**Barcode (5)**: draw a barcode inspection region for PCB serial-number "
"traceability."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:223
msgid "**DIP 焊点工具**：绘制 DIP 插件焊点检测区域。"
msgstr ""
"**DIP Solder**: draw a DIP through-hole solder-joint inspection region."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:224
msgid "**桥接工具**：绘制独立桥接（连锡）检测区域，可置于元件旁。"
msgstr ""
"**Bridge**: draw a standalone solder-bridge inspection region — place it "
"next to the component."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:225
msgid "**焊盘沾胶工具（8）**：绘制焊盘沾红胶检测区域。"
msgstr ""
"**Glue on Pad (8)**: draw an inspection region for red glue on the solder "
"pad."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:226
msgid "**颜色工具（9）**：绘制通用颜色区域检测框。"
msgstr "**Color (9)**: draw a general-purpose color-region inspection box."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:228
msgid "关于快捷键，参考 :ref:`编程页面快捷键`"
msgstr "Keyboard reference: see :ref:`编程页面快捷键`."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:231
msgid "常见封装编程示例"
msgstr "Common-package programming examples"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:234
msgid "电容、电阻"
msgstr "Capacitors and resistors"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:238
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:268
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:328
msgid "步骤："
msgstr "Steps:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:237
msgid "选择\"本体工具\"框出元件主体区域（紧贴真实外廓，尽量减少空白）。"
msgstr ""
"Pick the **Body** tool and box the component body (hug the actual outline; "
"keep blank space to a minimum)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:238
msgid "选择\"焊料工具\"分别框出左右（或多端）焊盘/焊点区域；"
msgstr ""
"Pick the **Solder** tool and box each pad / solder-joint area (left, right, "
"or all ends)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:246
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:281
msgid "质量建议："
msgstr "Quality tips:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:241
msgid "本体框贴合元件实际形状，避免包含过多空白区域；"
msgstr ""
"Have the body box hug the actual component shape; avoid including too much "
"blank space."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:242
msgid "焊料框应该紧贴焊料的爬锡区域；"
msgstr "Have the solder box hug the solder fillet area."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst
msgid "手动编程电容、电阻示意"
msgstr "Manual programming — capacitor and resistor illustration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:248
msgid "分组与属性： 使用\"选择工具\"框选主体与全部焊料框 → 右键 \"将选中的特征分组为新元件\" 生成一个元件，填写："
msgstr ""
"Grouping and properties: use the **Select** tool to drag-select the body box"
" and every solder box → right-click → **Group selection as new component** "
"to create a component, filling in:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:251
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:286
msgid "标识（必填，建议与丝印一致）"
msgstr "Designator (required; should match the silkscreen)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:252
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:287
msgid "（可选）料号 / 封装"
msgstr "Part number / package (optional)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:253
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:288
msgid "（可选）备注或版本号"
msgstr "Notes or revision number (optional)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:255
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:290
msgid "点击\"创建新元件\"完成。"
msgstr "Click **Create New Component** to finish."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:263
msgid "QFP 封装 IC 芯片"
msgstr "QFP-packaged IC"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:266
msgid "选择\"本体工具\"框出芯片主体（紧贴封装外沿）。"
msgstr "Pick the **Body** tool and box the IC body (hug the package outline)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:267
msgid "选择\"IC 引脚工具\"框出任意一侧整排引脚（覆盖焊盘 + 焊料 + 引脚末端区域）。"
msgstr ""
"Pick the **IC Lead** tool and box one full row of leads — the box must cover"
" the pad, the solder, and the lead tip."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:268
msgid "右键\"复制\"该引脚框，拖动至对侧或其它边；必要时使用右键旋转使其与该边引脚方向一致。"
msgstr ""
"Right-click → **Copy** the lead box, drag the copy to the opposite side or "
"another edge, and right-click rotate to align with that edge's lead "
"direction."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:271
msgid "框贴合元件实际形状，避免包含过多空白区域；"
msgstr ""
"Have the box hug the actual component shape; avoid including too much blank "
"space."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:277
msgid ""
"(2D) IC 引脚检测需要划分 3 个区域：焊盘、焊料、引脚末端；参见 :ref:`IC 引脚检测 2D v2（Lead 2D v2，基于颜色比例）`"
" 以了解区域划分标准。"
msgstr ""
"2D IC-lead inspection splits the lead region into three zones — pad, solder,"
" and lead tip. See :ref:`IC 引脚检测 2D v2（Lead 2D v2，基于颜色比例）` for how the zones"
" are split."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:288
msgid "分组与属性："
msgstr "Grouping and properties:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:284
msgid "使用\"选择工具\"框选主体与全部焊料框 → 右键 \"将选中的特征分组为新元件\" 生成一个元件，填写："
msgstr ""
"Use the **Select** tool to drag-select the body and every solder box → "
"right-click → **Group selection as new component** and fill in:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:297
msgid "SOP/TSSOP 封装的存储芯片或驱动芯片"
msgstr "SOP / TSSOP memory or driver IC"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:299
msgid "与 QFP 类似：本体工具框主体 → IC 引脚工具框一侧引脚后复制到另一侧 → 分组创建元件。"
msgstr ""
"Same as QFP: use the **Body** tool for the body, the **IC Lead** tool to box"
" one side of leads then copy to the other, and group them into a component."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst
msgid "SOP/TSSOP 封装示例"
msgstr "SOP / TSSOP example"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:307
msgid "私有库"
msgstr "Private library"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:309
msgid "编程好的元件可以添加至私有库，方便后续在其它产品中复用。"
msgstr ""
"A programmed component can be added to the private library for reuse on "
"other products."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:312
msgid "选择已编程好的元件，右键唤出菜单，点击\"添加到私有库\"。"
msgstr ""
"Select a programmed component, right-click, and pick **Add to Private "
"Library**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst
msgid "私有库示意"
msgstr "Private library illustration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:321
msgid "在弹出的对话框中填写元件的封装、料号，点击\"添加到私有库\"完成添加。"
msgstr ""
"In the dialog that appears, fill in the package and part number, then click "
"**Add to Private Library**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:323
msgid "在\"私有库\"页面可以选择元件模板, 点击 ``使用此模板`` 来添加到视图，或者删除库里的元件。"
msgstr ""
"On the **Private Library** page you can pick a template and click **Use this"
" template** to add it to the view, or delete library entries."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:331
msgid "训练与评估"
msgstr "Training and evaluation"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:333
msgid "确认全部元件后点击 ``训练`` ，耗时 ~1 分钟；完成后点击 ``自动生成检测参数`` 来基于所有元件的训练集数据分布生成检测参数。"
msgstr ""
"Once every component is confirmed, click **Train** — it takes about a "
"minute. When training finishes, click **Auto-generate Inspection "
"Parameters** to derive parameters from the dataset distribution across all "
"components."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:-1
msgid "训练示意"
msgstr "Training illustration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:339
msgid "点击下方的\"评估全部\"按钮，对所有元件进行评估，（绿=模型预测正确 / 红=模型预测与实际不符）。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Evaluate All** below to evaluate every component (green = model "
"prediction matches; red = model prediction disagrees with the label)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:343
msgid "**训练常见问题：**"
msgstr "**Common training questions:**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:345
msgid "**训练成功后开始测试又显示需要训练**：再点一次 *训练* 按钮；检查列表中是否有空元件（缺少检测算法）。"
msgstr ""
"**Training succeeded but starting an inspection prompts for training "
"again**: click **Train** once more; also check the list for empty components"
" (components with no inspection algorithm assigned)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:346
msgid ""
"**第一次训练耗时很长（约 10 分钟）**：i7-8 代工控机首次训练约 2.5 分钟属正常，第二次及之后会显著加快。等待训练正常结束即可。"
msgstr ""
"**First training takes a long time (around 10 minutes)**: on an i7-8th-gen "
"IPC, the first training run normally takes about 2.5 minutes; subsequent "
"runs are significantly faster. Wait for training to finish."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:347
msgid ""
"**训练失败原因不明**：检查训练集中是否有反馈图片越界（被切掉一部分），删除该图重新训练；若是停电 / "
"异常关机后出现，数据库可能损坏，可重新创建产品后再训练。"
msgstr ""
"**Training fails for no obvious reason**: check the training set for "
"feedback images that fall outside the board (partially cropped) and delete "
"them, then retrain. If the failure follows a power outage or unclean "
"shutdown, the database may be corrupted — recreate the product and retrain."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:354
msgid "后续：不健康项可参考 :ref:`检测参数` 章节按需微调；修改或补录后重新训练+评估即可迭代。"
msgstr ""
"Next steps: tune any unhealthy items as described in :ref:`检测参数`; after "
"edits or additions, re-train and re-evaluate to iterate."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:356
msgid "**导入 CAD**"
msgstr "**Import CAD**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:358
msgid ""
"页面顶部工具栏提供 **导入 CAD** 按钮，等价于自动编程向导第 5 步的 CAD 上传功能。可在产品已编程后再次导入 CAD，把丝印 / 料号 /"
" 封装 / 坐标 / 旋转角度等批量更新到现有元件上，无需重新走一次自动编程。详细的 CAD 文件格式与字段映射请参见 :ref:`自动编程`。"
msgstr ""
"The top toolbar exposes an **Import CAD** button — equivalent to the CAD-"
"upload step (step 5) of the Auto-Programming wizard. Reimport CAD after the "
"product is programmed to batch-update existing components with designator / "
"part number / package / coordinates / rotation, without re-running Auto-"
"Programming. CAD file format and field mapping are covered in :ref:`自动编程`."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:360
msgid "**元件对齐 开关**"
msgstr "**Component Alignment switch**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/manual_programming.rst:362
msgid ""
"模板编辑器右上角的 **元件模板（Component Template）** 面板内提供 **元件对齐** "
"开关。开启时，使用该模板的所有元件在检测时会执行 AI 对齐（在允许偏移范围内自动校正位置）；关闭时跳过 AI "
"对齐、按金板坐标直接定位。建议大体积或贴装稳定的元件保持开启；可变体（替代料）或经常偏斜的元件根据现场效果决定。详见 :ref:`元件配置`。"
msgstr ""
"The **Component Template** panel at the top-right of the Template Editor "
"carries a **Component Alignment** switch. When on, every component using "
"this template runs AI alignment at inspection time (auto-correcting position"
" within the allowed shift range); when off, AI alignment is skipped and the "
"component is positioned directly by golden-board coordinates. Keep it on for"
" large or stably-mounted components; for alternative components or "
"components that frequently skew, decide based on on-site results. See "
":ref:`元件配置`."

